\begin_inset Formula $h:\left(s_{1},s_{2},\ldots,s_{i},\ldots s_{k-1}\right)\mapsto\left(s_{1},s_{2},\ldots,s_{i-1},0,s_{i},\ldots s_{k-1}\right)$
\end_inset

, ta có:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{alignat*}{1}
c_{i,0}^{*}\alpha & =\left(c\circ h\right)^{*}\alpha\\
 & =h^{*}\left(c^{*}\alpha\right)\\
 & =h^{*}\left(\sum_{i=1}^{k}f_{i}dt_{1}dt_{2}\cdots\widehat{dt_{i}}\cdots dt_{k}\right).
\end{alignat*}

\end_inset

Với 
\begin_inset Formula $j\neq i$
\end_inset

